            <h2 id="what-heading" class="reveal-up font-heading font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-brand-900 tracking-tight mb-5">What is an Awning <span class="text-brand-500">Window?</span></h2>
            <p class="reveal-up text-lg text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              An awning window is <strong class="text-slate-700">hinged at the top</strong> and swings outward from the bottom using a crank handle. When open, the glass pane angles away from the wall like an awning — deflecting rain and debris while allowing fresh air to flow in from below.
